      "narration": "Each step cuts the remaining elements in half. The number of steps is log-base-two of n. Ten elements takes four steps. A million elements takes just twenty. A billion? Thirty steps. That's O(log n) time and O(1) space \u2014 no extra memory beyond three pointers.",
